title: Marvel Civil War Complete (reading order on ComicBookHerald)
description:
This is a compilation of the Marvel Civil War comics as listed on the 'Guide Part 7 (Civil War)' on the ComicBookHerald web site. Link is also in the torrent.

I have included all 4 Ghost Rider tie-ins even though, to date, the site does not include them.

There is also and Excel spreadsheet (for those who find it useful) of the entire list.

Enjoy reading!
